//! # Compliance Framework
//!
//! Static analysis for regulatory and industry compliance.
//!
//! ## Supported Standards
//!
//! - **MISRA C:2012** - Motor Industry Software Reliability Association
//! - **DO-178C** - Software Considerations in Airborne Systems
//! - **IEC 61508** - Functional Safety
//! - **ISO 26262** - Road vehicles Functional safety
//! - **CERT C/C++** - Secure coding standards
//!
//! ## Quick Start
//!
//! ```quanta
//! use quantalang::compliance::prelude::*;
//!
//! // Create automotive compliance checker
//! let profile = ComplianceProfile::automotive(Asil::C);
//! let checker = ComplianceChecker::new(CheckerConfig {
//!     profile,
//!     ..Default::default()
//! });
//!
//! // Check source file
//! let violations = checker.check_file("src/safety_critical.quanta")?;
//!
//! // Generate report
//! let report = checker.generate_report();
//! println!("{}", report.to_text());
//! ```

